## Development Rules

- **Docx Rule**: If working with `.docx` specs, run `npx mammoth` to convert to markdown first.
- **No gradients** — pure solid colors only (design philosophy).
- **Stitch design tokens** must be used (`bg-surface`, `text-on-surface`, `bg-primary`, etc.) — never hardcode hex in components.
- **Bootstrap is removed** — all UI must use Tailwind/Stitch utility classes.
- **Mobile-first always** — default is single-column full-width, use `sm:` to scale up.
- **Touch targets**: All buttons and interactive elements must be `min-h-[44px]` or `min-h-[48px]`.
- **Testing**: Algorithms are pure static functions. Test with xUnit in `TurnIt.Tests` project.

